        "=== DGX Spark NEXT standard available models ===\nPurpose: use the proven DGX photoreal NVFP4 structure, but remove references to files not currently present in this container.\n\nChanged on 2026-05-31:\n- CLIP: qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed.safetensors -> qwen_3_8b_bf16.safetensors because fp8mixed is not present.\n- Disabled r64 LoRA because klein_9B_Turbo_r64.safetensors is not present.\n- Model chain is now UNET nvfp4 -> r128 LoRA 0.45 -> SNOFS 0.35.\n- Flux2KleinEnhancer remains absent.\n- Two-stage sampler, ReferenceLatent, dpmpp_2m / sgm_uniform, SplitSigmas 6 are kept.\n\nThis is not a low-goal collapse-prevention workflow. It is the highest currently coherent workflow using only installed DGX assets.\nIf prompt following is still insufficient, install missing qwen_3_8b_fp8mixed and r64 LoRA, or move to an official Flux.2 9B base-edit subgraph rather than reviving Flux2KleinEnhancer."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
